imdb.title: Natholdet - med Anders Breinholt
plot: A late-night comedy talkshow focusing on daily unintentionally funny content from the media. In each episode Anders Breinholt welcomes a new celebrity co-host for the evening. Together they watch current clips from the media of the day.::Pineapple Entertainment
